spec_data.Name: emacs-goto-chg
spec_data.Description:
GotoChg is an add-on package for GNU Emacs. It allows to got to the point of
the most recent edit in then buffer. When repeated, go to the second most recent
edit, etc.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Tue 01 Aug 2017 04:16:10 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Emacs add-on to go to last change in current buffer
